Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"And that's when the yellow birdie\Nthought to himself:"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hm... My favorite little tree\Nisn't such a little tree anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.46,0:00:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"So she sang her song, big and strong."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"And they all lived in that great,\Nbig tree happily ever after."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.10,0:00:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The End.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you reading a bedtime story to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...an apple tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, bein' replanted in a whole\Nnew place is very upsettin' for a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.51,0:00:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And Bloomberg here is one of my favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair, Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a luxurious private\Nsleeper cart for a TREE...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...while I am crowded and cramped\Nin a same cart with all the other ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:00:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to get my beauty sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But Bloomberg's the whole\Nreason we're makin' this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.22,0:01:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs his rest so we can give him\Nas a gift to my relatives in Appleloosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk about it as if\Nit's your baby or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who you callin' a baby?! Bloomberg's no baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.14,0:01:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't wet wittle Rarity make you all saddie-waddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloomber's a big and strong apple tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.46,0:01:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he is. A coochie-coochie-coo-coo-coo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.52,0:01:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's widdle Rarity, who's all saddie-waddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,For crying out loud in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I was up early fire-roasting those snacks\Nyou're all eating and I pooped!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of, somebody's popcorn kernels didn't get popped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's time we all got a little shut-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a big day ahead of us tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Psst...! Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You asleep yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Are you asleep yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was sleeping, how could I\Nhave asked you if you were asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When we get to Appleloosa, you think\Nwe'll have to carry that heavy tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...all the way from the train to the orchard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What tree? You mean Bloomberg?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy's not a tree, silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash thinks Fluttershy is a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I do NOT think she's a tree. I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say she was a tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Well... yes. But not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know she's not a tree, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not a tree, Dashie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to be a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for Pete's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was kinda huffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huffy the Magic Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you all be quiet NOW?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloomberg?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloomberg!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I tend to snore a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A buffalo stampede!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I just love their accessories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're getting awfully close to the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, looky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they're going tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Ooh! Ooh! Now do a backflip!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Or... just jump?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Something tells me this isn't a circus act.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there! Where are you headed in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. You're pretty quick for someone so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...bulky. No offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanna know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got Bloomberg!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon-napping Spike. I'll show her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to AAAPPLELOOSA!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Braeburn, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, cousin Applejack. Mind your manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You have yet to introduce me\Nto your compadres. Shame on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Braeburn, listen. Somth'n terrible's happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrible is right. Your train is full seven minutes late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's seven minutes less for you to\Ndelight in the pleasures and wonders of...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,AAAPPLELOOSA!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Boggles the mind, we settler ponies built\Nall this in just a past year, don't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you can see, we have all of the finest comforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Like horse-drawn carriages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you pull now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, we just switched.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And now's there horse-drawn horse-drawn carriages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Braeburn, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's our local waterin' hole:\NThe Salt Block.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough salt for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't I at least get a glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there is the office of Sheriff Silverstar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's where we have our wild west dances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's where we have our mild west dances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But Braeburn, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And here is the most wonderful sight in all of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,AAAPPLELOOSA!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Our apple orchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Braeburn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,First harvest should be any day now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Braebu...\N-Good thing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-Brae...\N-Cause we need that grub to live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:07:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,BRAEBURN!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... yes, cous?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a very nice town n' all\Nbut we have a huuuge problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of our friends are missin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-A stampede of buffalo!\N-The took Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Rainbow Dash went after them!\N-And we can't find Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And we had an apple tree with us\Nfor your orchard, but they took that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say buffalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dem buffalo, they want us settler ponies to take\Nevery single tree you see here off this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure as hay don't want any new ones added in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We put a lotta hard work into this land so we\Ncould feed our town, our families, our foals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And now they're sayin' all these trees have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,T'ain't fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't wait to get my hooves\Non that little buffalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody tricks Rainbow Dash and gets away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you caught me! Looks like I tricked you\Nand didn't get away with it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh! What do you think you're doing?\NYou gotta get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna blow my cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm trying to save Spike!\N-OH MY GOSH! So am I!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And the more of us there are out here,\Nthe more chance is of us getting...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Pinkie. I'll hold them off. Save yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,STOP!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash, Pinkie, 'sup?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, no worries, I know those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so, Spike. Catch ya later, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems they took me by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And they feel awful about it too, poor guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, they totally respect dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...so they treat me like an honored guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Still don't like ponies much though,\Nbut you're with me, so it's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Why, I still don't trust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I say we turn tail and bail while we still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we finish eating?\NAre you a loco in the coco?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I please have more of that\Nmushy stuff, whatever it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly. And, Mr. Spike,\Nyou like gemstones, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Turquoise, mmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This here's Little Strongheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are my friends,\NPinkie Pie and Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! We are outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, accept my apologies\Nfor what happened on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't mean for anyone to be hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.82,0:10:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We only wanted the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The settler ponies have overtaken the land\Nand have planted an orchard all over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of their thoughtlessness, we can no longer\Nrun over our traditional stampeding grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's time they've met Chief Thunderhooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a long and winding stampeding trail...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...which we run upon for many generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My father stampeded upon these grounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...and his father before him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...and his father before him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...and his father before him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...and his father before him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-...and...\N-I think they get the idea, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a sacred tradition to run the path every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But these year, these settler ponies, these...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Appleloosans!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They planted apple trees all over it\Nwithout asking our permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not very nice. Right, Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The ponies refused to move their trees...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...so we are stuck here and it is not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See, Rainbow Dash? They had a good reason to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say they had a good reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! We have some apple-picking\NAppleloosans to talk to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Gently, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Rarity. But our friends are out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...and we have to be ready for a long hike\Ninto buffalo territory if we're gonna save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you escape from the buffalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We promised the buffalo a chance to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? 'bout what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought our new pal Little Strongheart\Nhere to explain to the Appleloosans...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...why they should move\Nthe apple trees off buffalo land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That information would be quite help...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird. Cause my cousin Braeburn\Nhere wants to explain to the buffalo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...why they should let the apple trees stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That would a useful thing to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The land is theirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You planted the trees not knowing that. Honest mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just gotta move 'em, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They busted their rumps here! And now\Nthey're supposed to bust their rumps again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...just cause some buffalo\Nwon't stampede someplace else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Plant the trees somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only flat land around these parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The buffalo had it FIRST!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The settler ponies need it to LIVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Both the settlers and the buffalo\Nhave good reasons to use this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be something we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I've got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We may be divided\NBut of you all I beg{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To remember we're all hoofed\NAt the end of each leg{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter what the issue\NCome from wherever you please{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All this fighting gets you nothing\NBut hoof-and-mouth disease{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Arguing's not the way\NHey, come out and play!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a shiny new day\NSo what do you say?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You gotta shaaare\NYou gotta caaare{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a right thing to do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You gotta shaaare\NYou gotta caaare{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And there'll always be a way through!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Both our diets, I should mention\NAre completely vegetarian{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We all eat hay and oats\NWhy be at each other's throat?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You gotta shaaare\NYou gotta caaare{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a right thing to do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And there'll always be a way throoough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Pinkie Pie, that was FANTASTIC!\NWhat a great song, you're right on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that Sheriff Silverstar\Nand I have come to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the worst performance we've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Absotively.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The time for action is upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Our stampede will start at high noon tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And if the orchard is still there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...we'll flatten it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And the whole town!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But Chief...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And we Appleloosans say you\Nbetter bring your best...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...cause we'll be ready and waitin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But Sheriff...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... That wasn't the message of my song at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I want my kin to have what they need to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...but a storm's a-brewin' here.\NAnd I don't like the look of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We've just got to talk some sense into them\Nbefore somepony gets hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, maybe if you would just reconsider, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,About the trees, now if you just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could just sit down and talk, we could...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't anybody be rational and reasonable?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheriff! If we could only...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there some way to stop this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless the settlers remove those trees...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...I do not think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you don't wanna do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But they have taken our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you have me do, Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. But it's never too late\Nto think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,At noon it will be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinkthinkthinkthinkthinkthinkthink!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You gotta shaaare\NYou gotta caaare{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a right thing to do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You gotta shaaare...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,CHAAARGE!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,FIRE!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I've got a much better idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We will allow the apple orchard to stay\Nin exchange for a share of its fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Those... delicious apple pies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather eat turquoise any day of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloomberg, this is your special day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama's so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Princess Celestia."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Friendship is a wondrous and powerful thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.02,0:21:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Even the worst of enemies can become friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"You need understanding and compromise."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.23,0:21:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"You've got to share. You've got to care."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! That's what I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Synced by Nathan2000\Nhttp://mlp.wikia.com/wiki/User:Nathan2000
